    "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dyftyrehc/image/upload/v1772261487/nmai-articles/rcjbgujbrwhnkxk2hzem.jpg",
    "alt": "Assam Chief Minister distributing land pattas under Mission Basundhara"
